en_132225_0	A student attached to the Sabaragamuwa University was killed last night after being run over by a bus in front of Gandara Police Station.
en_132225_1	The ill-fated bus was transporting a group of Joint Opposition supporters back home after their May Day rally.
en_132225_2	The 26-year-old victim of Gandara Talalla met was hit by the bus in front of the Gandara Police station.
en_132225_3	Police Media spokesman office stated that the driver of the bus was arrested this morning while he was in hiding.
